Ensemble", "qid": null, "roles": ["jazz_quintet"]}, {"id": "116764", "name": "Don Pate", "qid": null, "roles": ["double_bass"]}]}, {"label": "Selections (unspecified)", "work": "Selections (unspecified)", "composer": null, "performers": [{"id": "19756", "name": "Archie Shepp", "qid": "Q200791", "roles": ["tenor_saxophone"]}, {"id": "20955", "name": "Archie Shepp Quintet", "qid": null, "roles": ["jazz_quintet"]}]}], "quotes": [{"speaker": "Roy Haynes", "qid": "Q448235", "text": "Yeah. Some of it was headed that direction. That’s when I started getting the young audiences. Then I started – I had – I can’t even think of the guy’s name. He’s in California now. I had some good musicians. Some of them worked with Miles. I had some good cats there. I had some good times, too. When I had the name – we played once at Carnegie Hall with Tony Williams, with Lifetime, Archie Shepp, Weather Report, my group. We burnin’. We had a standing ovation. We went to Europe, Japan. I had a nice little run with it. But later on, after I stopped the Hip Ensemble, then they start calling my groups Hip Ensemble when they weren’t Hip Ensemble. The Hip Ensemble was that one period of time when I was using the title. After that, then they wanted it. At first it seemed like they didn’t want to accept the name. We would close with the black national anthem. I have a drum solo and go into that. Close, close out the show.", "caption": "1972 Carnegie Hall concert with Lifetime, Weather Report, and Shepp", "conf": "high", "first_person": true, "doc_title": "Roy Haynes — Smithsonian Jazz Oral History", "collection": "si", "url": "https://amhistory.si.edu/jazz/Haynes-Roy/Haynes_Roy_Transcript.pdf"}], "featured_people": [{"qid": "Q200791", "id": "19756", "name": "Archie Shepp"}, {"qid": "Q1236568", "id": "71842", "name": "Dom Um Romão"}, {"qid": "Q2188027", "id": "116753", "name": "Eric Gravatt"}, {"qid": "Q1331323", "id": "63792", "name": "George Adams"}, {"qid": "Q1412862", "id": "46302", "name": "Hannibal Peterson"}, {"qid": "Q188165", "id": "115906", "name": "Herb Bushler"}, {"qid": "Q44767", "id": "55350", "name": "Joe Zawinul"}, {"qid": "Q558162", "id": "70322", "name": "Miroslav Vitous"}, {"qid": "Q448235", "id": "49009", "name": "Roy Haynes"}, {"qid": "Q453604", "id": "22342", "name": "Tony Williams"}, {"qid": "Q317161", "id": "43976", "name": "Wayne Shorter"}]}